text:
PH COVID-19 CASES BREACH 80,000. DOH announces on Sunday, 2,110 additional #COVID19 cases. Philippines now has 80,448 total confirmed coronavirus infections, as of July 26.

Of the total cases, 52,406 are active cases
382 new recoveries; 26,110 total
39 new deaths; 1,932 total https://t.co/nkMQfc9bY7
